Barroso Says EU Must Solve Debt Crisis to Restore Confidence

-- B y   J a m e s   G .   N e u g e r
-- 
2011-10-17T10:43:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-17/barroso-says-eu-must-solve-debt-crisis-to-restore-confidence.html
European leaders are under pressure
to restore confidence in the euro area economy, European
Commission President  Jose Barroso  said.  Labor and employer leaders today pressed governments “to
do whatever is necessary to protect the financial stability of
the euro zone, to restore confidence in the euro zone and in the
European Union,” Barroso told reporters in Brussels today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James G. Neuger at 
 jneuger@bloomberg.net  